## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to design geo-distributed, multi-region sharded stores with online rebalancing, clear read/write paths, and failure handling.

## Key Concepts

- Consistent hashing for shard mapping
- Tenant isolation and data locality
- Cross-region replication and latency trade-offs
- Online shard rebalancing with minimal downtime
- Read/write path and quorum settings under regional outages

## Code Example

```javascript
// Pseudo-config for shard routing
const SHARD_COUNT = 200;
function shardForTenant(tenantId) {
  // hash to shard index
  return hash(tenantId) % SHARD_COUNT;
}
```

