## Why This Is Asked
This question probes practical sharding and cross-region replication decisions under high throughput, tenant isolation, and online migrations. It also assesses failure handling and testing strategies.

## Key Concepts
- Shard key design (hash vs range)
- Cross-region replication with quorum reads/writes
- Online shard rebalancing and migration safety
- Hot-tenant management and autosplitting
- Testing: load testing and chaos engineering

## Code Example
```javascript
// shard key sketch
function shardKey(tenantId, eventType) {
  const base = tenantId + ":" + eventType;
  const hash = require('crypto').createHash('sha256').update(base).digest('hex');
  return hash.substring(0, 16);
}
```

